text: ── Sorry, Mano! I kept you waiting.

Well, I stopped by a little shop, and when I handed them
my business card to ask for a receipt, they seemed surprised.

They said they've never seen a talent agency around here
before. Asked what we do, why we're in this town... You know.

I see... Hehe,
thank you for your hard work.

When you meet someone who works in a field you're not
familiar with, you can't help but want to ask them questions...

Yeah, I get that feeling, but... Well, time's
running short. Let's hurry to the next location.
